<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Mahogany</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Mahogany is one of the newest neighbourhoods in Calgary, with development approved and beginning in 2007.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Bordered to the north by Copperfield, the two communities share a joint community atmosphere and maintain close ties to one another.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">With a master plan in place, the community in Mahogany attracts buyers from all walks of life.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in mahogany comprise mainly of single family retreat like units, some of which even enjoy the luxury of spectacular lake views of the Mahogany Lake.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">With continued development today, Mahogany is bound to thrive, because as Avenue Magazine once said, it's <span class="par-xl">“A small, lakeside community with big plans.”</span></p>
        </div>
